=== [[Season 1]] ===
[[Illyrio Mopatis]] gives [[Daenerys Targaryen]] a wedding gift of three [[dragon]] eggs, said to be from the Shadow Lands beyond Asshai.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Winter is Coming]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

On their travel east, Ser [[Jorah Mormont]] tells Daenerys that the Shadow Lands are said to be covered by &quot;[[ghost grass]]&quot;, a form of grass that, in [[Dothraki]] mythology, will overrun the green grass of the [[Dothraki Sea]] and spell the end of the world.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Kingsroad]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

=== [[Season 2]] ===
During her stay in [[Qarth]], [[Daenerys Targaryen|Daenerys]] encounters [[Quaithe]], a mysterious woman hailing from the Shadow Lands.
